Description:
OUTSTANDING OPPORTUNITY WITH EXPONENTIAL POTENTIAL!!
LJ Hooker is proud to present this super rare and once in a lifetime opportunity in the heart of Dandenong. Sitting on approximately 2900m2 of prime soil, this property holds exponential future potential for development. Now is the time to take advantage of this goldmine and secure your long-term future.
This apartment complex is superbly maintained with outstanding tenants providing you with a stress free rental income of $210,000 approx per annum.
All 18 apartments are fully leased, each apartment offers two spacious bedrooms, one bathroom and one allocated carport. Each apartment is separately titled, providing you with the benefit to sell individually in the future.
Located across the road from Dandenong High School you are only within a short distance to Dandenong Plaza/Market, Dandenong Hospital, Chisholm Tafe, Dandenong North Primary School, freeway access, public transport, recreational facilities and all that Dandenong has to offer.
Call Ben Jusufi or Geoffrey Reis for any further information!

Description:
QUALITY LIVING IN PRIME LOCATION!!
LJ Hooker is proud to present this wonderful opportunity for all First Home Buyers, astute investors and buyers looking to downsize. Only 12 years young and full of quality, this home is ready for you to move in to right away. Situated in a peaceful pocket of Dandenong, this home provides the ideal and convenient lifestyle you have been searching for. Currently tenanted until August 2018 for $1343 pcm.
Offering 3 good-sized bedrooms with BIR, master with ensuite and WIR, dining/meals area which is adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped gas cooking, s/s appliances, dishwasher and an abundance of cupboard space. The main bathroom and laundry make up the interior of this magnificent home.
Features of this home include: 2nd living area, ducted heating, security alarm system, single lockup garage and garden shed.
Located within a short distance to Dandenong West Primary School, Dandenong High School, Princes highway, Dandenong Plaza/Market, freeway access, public transport, parks and recreational facilities and all that Dandenong has to offer.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!!

Description:
TWO HOMES WITH MANY OPTIONS!
Earn a dual income while planning your development (STCA) OR move in if you are two families looking to live close to each other OR live in one and rent out the other OR an excellent addition to your investment portfolio.
Centrally located and within 5 minutes of the train station, these two separately Titled homes are on a combined block of 839m2 with a frontage of approximately 21m.
Each home offers three bedrooms, formal lounge, meals area off the kitchen, undercover entertainment area, main bathroom, large laundry with access to a separate shower room and a separate toilet.
Externally, No. 14 offers a lockup garage, carport and extensively concreted area while No. 16 offers a semi-double garage with access to a large storeroom area.
Both homes have additional secure parking spaces behind the lockable gates, which is a bonus when living in the heart of the city.
DO YOUR SUMS & SEAL THE DEAL!

Description:
Live In, Invest or Redevelop, The Choice is Yours
Situated in one of central Dandenong’s most sought after pockets this property caters for families seeking convenient living, investors/small developers wanting to capture the growth of Dandenong and even 2 families or generations wanting a terrific dual occupancy site with approved plans and permit for townhouses and single storey unit. Sitting on a decent block of 592 sqm (approx.) the neatly presented home provides an open planned living, meals and kitchen area, 3 bedrooms, updated central bathroom, polished timber flooring throughout, central gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling and good sized garage with adjoining shed. With fully approved plans and permit for the construction of 1 double storey, 3 bedroom plus study, 3 bathrooms and single lock up garage with independent driveway access and 1 single storey, 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom and single garage unit in the rear, this project is perfect for 2 generations to live in the same spot but still have their own space. Literally a short stroll to Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong High School, Chisholm TAFE and public transport services as well as easy access to Plaza and Market, this property is perfectly located to capture everything great that Dandenong has to offer yet remains in a quiet and family friendly street. Do not miss this amazing opportunity as homes in this pocket always attract great interest. Make sure you view this home before it is too late.
Contact: Neb Delibasic on 0411 332 467

Description:
Location and Lifestyle
First home or investment, there is no compromise in this ground floor home nestled in the prestigious Metro Village and highly sought after central pocket of Dandenong, overlooking a stunning recreational park and Dandenong Creek Trail.
Offering 2 bedrooms with built in robes, study, large open plan living with direct access to a private rear yard, fully equipped kitchen with an island bench, sparkling central bathroom and a remote controlled garage. Other features includes mirrored robes to master, split level air-conditioner, electric wall heaters, alarm system and a dishwasher.
Located very close to Dandenong Station, Plaza, Market, variety of cafes and restaurants, choice of Pre-Schools, Primary Schools and High Schools, interstate bus services, Dandenong bypass, East Link Freeway and Princes Highway.
Currently tenanted on a periodic lease with a rental return of $1,455 per calendar month.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity.

QUALITY , DESIGN, LIFESTYLE
A spectacular achievement in design and floor plan, this stylish double story residence located in sort after James Street close to schools is a must see property.
Approx 15 years young this beauty has all the comforts and spaciousness looked into by any deserving family. Ground floor comprises 2 light filled contemporary living areas , open plan kitchen dining opening towards private courtyard, well spacious gourmet kitchen with lots of cupboards and dishwasher, large room/office with external access, separate bathroom/toilet and remote double garage with internal access.
First floor comprises rumpus room, lavish master bedroom with ensuite & walk-in robe, 3 more bedrooms with built in robes. End of the hallway you will find a balcony overlooking glorious views. You have more features and comforts such as carpets and tiles through out, ducted heating, rivers cycle heating cooling, ducted heating, down lights, high ceilings and much more.
Location speaks itself within moments away from primary and secondary schools, hospital, medical centre, 7-11 fuel station, convenience stores and close to freeway and eastlink.
Come experience the difference of living in this delightful central Dandenong home. MUST BE SOLD. VENDOR SAYS SELL
